author: David Ng, David Ng
title: Rob Reiner Appears to Suggest Trump Could Be Accessory to Murder over Coronavirus Response
description: Filmmaker Rob Reiner appeared to suggest that President Donald Trump could be an accessory to murder over his response to the coronavirus pandemic.
content:
Filmmaker Rob Reiner appeared to suggest that President Donald Trump could be an accessory to murder over his response to the coronavirus pandemic. The Princess Bride director also seemed to repeat the falsehood that Trump called the coronavirus a “hoax.”
